room_title: Escape room "Cabin" by Amazing Escape in Atlanta
room_address: 6040 Unity Dr Suite C, Norcross, GA 30071
room_description: Hiking in the woods, you and your friends notice an abandoned-looking shelter. Led by curiosity, you take a peek inside the cabin. Suddenly you are trapped inside by the psycho owner, who went out to buy supplies to hide your bodies forever... Will you escape before he returns?
